code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     String remotePath = DropboxHelper.getRemotePath(configuration, exchange).     String newRemotePath = DropboxHelper.getNewRemotePath(configuration, exchange).     DropboxConfigurationValidator.validateMoveOp(remotePath, newRemotePath).     DropboxMoveResult result = new DropboxAPIFacade(configuration.getClient(), exchange).move(remotePath, newRemotePath).     exchange.getIn().setHeader(DropboxResultHeader.MOVED_PATH.name(), result.getOldPath()).     exchange.getIn().setBody(result.getNewPath()).     log.debug("Moved from {} to {}", remotePath, newRemotePath). }
